OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FDavid Kogan, the first chair of
OL,7,Ffootball's inaugural regulator, has
OL,8,Fsaid he will take whatever action is
OL,9,Fnecessary to resolve the uncertainty
OL,10,Fsurrounding Sheffield Wednesday, in an
OL,11,Finterview with ITV News Sports Editor
OL,12,FSteve Scott.
OL,14,FThe boss of football's new watchdog
OL,15,Fsays he will force owners to sell up
OL,16,Fif they become a risk to the future of
OL,17,Fthe clubs they run.
