OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FDavid Kogan, the first chair of
OL,7,Ffootball's inaugural regulator,
OL,8,Faddressed the uncertainty surrounding
OL,9,FSheffield Wednesday in a wide-ranging
OL,10,Finterview with ITV News.
OL,12,FPlayers and staff at the Championship
OL,13,Fside, owned by Thai businessman
OL,14,FDejphon Chansiri, are yet to be paid
OL,15,FSeptember's wages, and the club is
OL,16,Foperating under the threat of fines or
OL,17,Fa points deduction for breaches of
OL,18,FEnglish Football League (EFL) rules.
