OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FFans continue to stage weekly
OL,7,Fprotests, fearing the club could fold
OL,8,Faltogether.
OL,10,F''Let's be clear. Sheffield Wednesday
OL,11,Fwas not only a founder of the first
OL,12,Ffootball league in this country, it
OL,13,Fwas also a founder of the Premier
OL,14,FLeague," Kogan told ITV News.
OL,16,F''We've been talking to supporters
OL,17,Fgroups, we've been talking to local
OL,18,Fpoliticians, we've been talking to the
OL,19,FEFL almost on a daily basis about
OL,20,Fwhat's actually going on there.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/16
