OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,F''We'll take whatever action we deem
OL,7,Fto be necessary. So we are on it. We
OL,8,Fabsolutely understand the importance
OL,9,Fof Sheffield Wednesday.
OL,11,F''There's no real question of the club
OL,12,Fgoing under unless action is taken by
OL,13,Fthe EFL to force it under. And I don't
OL,14,Fthink they're going to do that.
OL,16,F''We are going to address the issues
OL,17,Fwith the owner; we'll see what his
OL,18,Fresponse is when we do, and if he
OL,19,Fdoesn't do anything, we'll take
OL,20,Faction."
