OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FAnd that action could mean instructing
OL,7,FChansiri to sell. ''Depending on the
OL,8,Fevidence, we'll take a judgment once
OL,9,Fwe've got the evidence," Kogan said.
OL,11,FDavid Kogan said he will give the
OL,12,FPremier League and the EFL a limited
OL,13,Ftime to agree to a deal.
OL,15,FThe regulator holds wide-ranging
OL,16,Fpowers, which could increase in
OL,17,Fbreadth in the coming years.
