OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FOne of Kogan's current
OL,7,Fresponsibilities is rooting out
OL,8,Fpotential rogue owners from buying
OL,9,Finto English football in the first
OL,10,Fplace, but this is based on financial
OL,11,Fsustainability and does not extend to
OL,12,Fmaking judgments about, for example, a
OL,13,Fnation state's human rights record.
OL,15,F''The issue of overseas owners, the
OL,16,Fissue of ethical questions, is
OL,17,Fdeliberately not in our remit. We have
OL,18,Fno particular power or brief to make a
OL,19,Fvalue judgment,'' he said.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G6/16
