OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,F"What we do have is much more
OL,7,Fextensive powers than the Premier
OL,8,FLeague and the EFL to investigate
OL,9,Fpotential owners... So I think we will
OL,10,Fhave a much clearer view of owners as
OL,11,Fthey're coming in. But the ethical
OL,12,Fissues in terms of there being a
OL,13,Fforeign government or whatever, and
OL,14,Fnot our purview."
OL,16,FCounterintuitively, Kogan points to so-
OL,17,Fcalled 'good owners' as being a threat
OL,18,Fto the survival of some clubs, an
OL,19,Fissue he says he heard time and again
OL,20,Fat a meeting of more than one hundred
OL,21,Fclub bosses in Manchester on Wednesday.
