OL,6,FHe said: ''The lower down the league
OL,7,Fyou go, the more they're worried about
OL,8,Fwhether they're going to survive.
OL,9,FPeople talk about rogue owners or bad
OL,10,Fowners. I actually think in football,
OL,11,Fwhat we need to be more concerned
OL,12,Fabout, in some ways, are good owners.
OL,13,FGood owners who are spending money on
OL,14,Ftheir clubs, in their local towns, and
OL,15,Fstill losing money, with huge amounts
OL,16,Fof debt."
OL,18,FSo why not let clubs go to the wall if
OL,19,Fthey're badly run?
