OL,6,F''If you're going to apply the normal
OL,7,Frules of business in the world of
OL,8,Ffootball, I think you're going to have
OL,9,Fa very difficult time thinking normal
OL,10,Frules pertain - almost every club in
OL,11,Fthe pyramid has debt," Kogan said.
OL,13,F''If you're running a normal,
OL,14,Fsuccessful business, you're trying to
OL,15,Favoid having debt. Most clubs don't
OL,16,Fmake a profit. If you're running a
OL,17,Fsuccessful business, and I've run a
OL,18,Ffew, you're trying to make a profit.
OL,19,FFootball doesn't work on the normal
OL,20,Frules of business."
