OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,FThe Premier League and EFL have long
OL,7,Fdisagreed about the way wealth is
OL,8,Fdistributed through the football
OL,9,Fpyramid, and still have not hammered
OL,10,Fout a deal.
OL,12,FKogan says he will give them a very
OL,13,Flimited time frame to work out these
OL,14,Fdifferences; otherwise, he will impose
OL,15,Fa financial settlement on the parties.
OL,17,F"I am hoping that the world of
OL,18,Ffootball comes to its senses," he said.
