OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,F''Instead of failing to do a deal, as
OL,7,Fit did in 2023, 2025, we can help
OL,8,Fgrease the wheel so they get to one,
OL,9,Fwhich is sensible, and everybody can
OL,10,Fsign off on it.
OL,12,F"As I told them yesterday, we're
OL,13,Fworking on a guillotine timetable.
OL,14,FThere will be discussions starting in
OL,15,Fthe very near future, which will take
OL,16,Fplace over the course of a few months,
OL,17,Fbut no more than a few months.
