OL,6,F"At the end of it, if we have to, we
OL,7,Fcan impose a deal. I absolutely do not
OL,8,Fwant that to happen, because I think
OL,9,Fthe idea that we come in and slap a
OL,10,Fdeal on football isn't particularly
OL,11,Fdesirable, but we have the powers and
OL,12,Flegislation to do a number of things,
OL,13,Fand if we have to, we'll use those
OL,14,Fpowers."
