OL,6,FThe Premier League vehemently opposed
OL,7,Fthe very idea of an independent
OL,8,Fregulator.
OL,10,F''(They) expressed concerns about
OL,11,Fwhether we're going to meddle in its
OL,12,Fcommerciality and its ability to grow,
OL,13,Fsomething I've absolutely no desire to
OL,14,Fmeddle in whatsoever," Kogan said.
OL,16,FBut he believes that the battle is
OL,17,Fdone and they can now work well
OL,18,Ftogether.
