OL,6,F''I won't go into a private WhatsApp,
OL,7,Fbut I got a very, very congratulatory
OL,8,FWhatsApp from the chief executive of
OL,9,Fthe Premier League after the meeting
OL,10,Fyesterday, where he talks about the
OL,11,Fstrength of my executive team - which
OL,12,Fis very good - and he talked about the
OL,13,Ffact that we are now working together
OL,14,Fvery closely to find solutions," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F''The Premier League fought its fight
OL,18,Ffor the regulator not to exist. But
OL,19,Fthat fight is over. We're now in a
OL,20,Fdifferent place.''
