OL,6,FThis week, UEFA reluctantly sanctioned
OL,7,Ftwo league games in Italy and Spain to
OL,8,Fbe played overseas.
OL,10,FKogan says the Premier League is not
OL,11,Fdiscussing taking fixtures abroad, but
OL,12,Fany attempts would attract the
OL,13,Fscrutiny of the regulator.
OL,15,F''Part of my brief is the heritage of
OL,16,Fthe game," he said.
