OL,3,CFootball regulator pledges action to
OL,4,Csolve Sheffield Wednesday crisis
OL,6,F"You have to ask questions about
OL,7,Fwhether heritage, again, is reinforced
OL,8,Fif home games are being played in
OL,9,FPhiladelphia, rather than Liverpool.
OL,10,FSo, I think that we haven't got a
OL,11,Fclear view on this as a regulator. I
OL,12,Fknow the Premier League has got a
OL,13,Fclear view on it, and I welcome that
OL,14,Fview. And beyond that, you know we're
OL,15,Fwaiting for events.''
OL,17,F"I have no doubt the fans will have a
OL,18,Fview about where home games are
OL,19,Fplayed. And guess what, most of them
OL,20,Fwill want home games to be played at
OL,21,Fhome."
